{"tid":101301,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[蝴蝶]折左翼仲有冇得救","createTime":"2017-01-30T16:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T21:08:31.000Z","uid":69137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09903ad850806500602950c187e01c4c3ef02478","tid":101301,"uid":69137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"話說今朝出門口嘅時候見到地下有隻蝴蝶 行近望望原來未死 但係折左翼 飛唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就諗同用報紙兜佢上啲菊花度 廢事俾屋企人踩死<br />\n本身都好怕昆蟲 捉佢果陣仲亂飛 仲飛落我隻手度 嚇鳩死<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6C291e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6C291e.jpg&h=871e9078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/005002_831c7f1eedabe3b5706c91c46a69acbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F005002_831c7f1eedabe3b5706c91c46a69acbe.jpg&h=4d34dff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩返到屋企唔見左佢 搵左陣原來係車底<br />\n見落雨濕就再救起佢放去啲冇風 有野遮嘅地方<br />\n點知佢好有乖咁我一用報紙就自動行上去 好似好有靈性咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搖極都唔落菊花度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zx2LrT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zx2LrT.jpg&h=db5d3b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知佢除左花蜜仲有咩食, 仲有冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633812218dc320dfad39031a343805671910b257","tid":101301,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681f912346c4e6a5d869f27f4c0266ec6f49588e","tid":101301,"uid":69137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"宜家放左入個鞋盒度, 唔多點郁, 等聽朝再陽光再睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f26b56ba9e408c74d81af92d96d86cbe599eb2","tid":101301,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"本身都好短命<br />\n仲要斷左翼 好快玩完 rip"},{"pid":"f2becb1a2396a59b5ad675223988023c2fc76a55","tid":101301,"uid":63426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:17:15.000Z","msg":"無嫁喇，對翼唔會生返<br />\n基本上等死，佢本身成蟲左都唔長命<br />\n要養佢就用蜜糖加啲水搞均放係個長啲闊啲既碟度<br />\n佢口器太長，如果你個碟太短會食唔到"},{"pid":"7c3fb59825944c7a80f664f32e4a91fab8204cb6","tid":101301,"uid":69137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"唔係下嘛 咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38f36d24c17dd8b04c5607f5c9d6380977d282a","tid":101301,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T20:47:28.000Z","msg":"我通常拎嚟餵蜘蛛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e577af2ffc90906fe5ceaaaad92ef336115b32","tid":101301,"uid":70208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T21:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/050055_7e818c8fc2d75cfe012534ea066c6cda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F050055_7e818c8fc2d75cfe012534ea066c6cda.jpg&h=13d2af85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報喜斑粉蝶，佢可能同你報喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f211ef411055a97551a2da74fe9e063b6141f2","tid":101301,"uid":61542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T21:08:31.000Z","msg":"一個禮拜完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}